name: Harry Bronson

name: Harry Bronson
text: To me, our society has always struggled to find a way to work through its injustices to a place of justice, equity, and fairness. The call for that work has been brought forward by those who protest and make others uncomfortable, that has been our past and is our present.

name: Harry Bronson

name: Harry Bronson
text: From social and economic injustice, to systematic racism and oppression, to the neglect of the institutions we built to ensure trust and equality. We must work together and seek to bring about meaningful change.

text: And, for all those who have suffered by our delay to take action, we must reach out our hands and work with them against this common enemy. We can ignore the voices of change no longer.
